---
description: Pattern JSON files
globs: public/patterns/**/*.json
---

- Validate against `PatternV1Schema` from `types/pattern.ts`
- IDs must be kebab-case, unique across library
- `index.json` lists all patterns with id, name, author, license
- SVG in `tile.svg` must use allowed elements only
- Defaults specify stitch/gap/stroke in mm
